# Styling and UI Framework

## CSS Framework
- **Bootstrap 5.3.3**: Main CSS framework for layouts and components
- **React Bootstrap**: React components with Bootstrap styling
- **Sass**: CSS preprocessor for custom styles in [styles/](mdc:styles)

## UI Component Libraries
- **React Bootstrap**: Pre-built Bootstrap components for React
- **Feather Icons**: [react-feather](mdc:https:/github.com/feathericons/react-feather) for consistent iconography
- **Custom Icons**: [components/Icons/](mdc:components/Icons) - Custom icon components

## Responsive Design
- **Bootstrap Grid**: 12-column responsive grid system
- **Breakpoints**: Mobile-first responsive design
- **Container Classes**: Bootstrap containers for consistent spacing

## Interactive Features
- **React Leaflet**: [components/Map/](mdc:components/Map) - Interactive maps
- **Drag & Drop**: [@dnd-kit](mdc:https:/dndkit.com) for sortable interfaces in [components/DnD/](mdc:components/DnD)
- **Parallax Scrolling**: react-scroll-parallax for visual effects
- **Toast Notifications**: Sonner library with [components/Alerts.tsx](mdc:components/Alerts.tsx)

## Form Styling
- **Formik**: Form handling with validation
- **React Bootstrap Forms**: Styled form components
- **Form Components**: [components/Form/](mdc:components/Form) - Custom form elements

## Gallery and Media
- **Masonry Layout**: [components/Masonry/](mdc:components/Masonry) - Pinterest-style layouts
- **Next.js Image**: Optimized image loading and responsive images
- **Gallery**: [pages/gallery.tsx](mdc:pages/gallery.tsx) - Photo gallery implementation

## Theme and Branding
- **Custom Sass**: Restaurant-specific styling
- **Bootstrap Customization**: Custom variables and overrides
- **Consistent Color Palette**: Brand colors throughout the application

## Performance
- **CSS Optimization**: Next.js automatic CSS optimization
- **Critical CSS**: Inline critical styles for faster loading
- **Image Optimization**: WebP and responsive images with Next.js
